  <text>
      <l>
        <orig>
            <k ji="京">きょう</k>にても</orig>
        <trans lang="en">Even in Kyoto</trans>
      </l>
      <l>
        <orig>
            <k ji="京">きょう</k>なつかしや</orig>
        <trans lang="en">To be longing for Kyoto:</trans>
      </l>
      <l>
        <orig>
            <k ji="時">ほとと</k>
            <k ji="鳥">ぎす</k>
         </orig>
        <trans lang="en">A cuckoo cuckoos.</trans>
      </l>
  </text>
  <commentary>
    <remarks>
      <p>Interestingly, hototogisu is a "time bird". This may give the verse an additional
        (if laconic) poignancy.</p>
    </remarks>
